{"tid":2041376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國考慮放寬BNO護照權利　葉劉淑儀認為措施溫和","createTime":"2020-05-29T07:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T08:18:13.000Z","uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28b72eadbfeff62689715142bc7d25a24872567f","tid":2041376,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"英國外相藍韜文早前表示考慮放寬英國國民海外護照(BNO)的簽證權利。新民黨主席葉劉淑儀認為措施非常溫和，因BNO護照持有人需有適當理由才能延長在英國的逗留期限。她說，假如港人想藉此獲取居英權，也必須在英國住滿5年，因此以海外護照移民是絕對不容易。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀說，即使現時「港區國安法」未有很多細節，但她不認同會造成大規模的移民潮，相信「港區國安法」的落實需符合《基本法》原則，在普通法制度下亦不容易定罪，市民毋須過分擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529120-20200529.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529120-20200529.htm&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33LScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=eed549ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529120-20200529.htm&h=0513590a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529120-20200529.htm</a>"},{"pid":"261b77810ee57060681b43a86e76a490c15d140e","tid":2041376,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"睇嚟班建制個個都支持BNO平權"},{"pid":"69cd9027f7f29b0e2e1cdfb8a84ccb585e99a402","tid":2041376,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"咪撚比班建制走呀 返大灣區啦"},{"pid":"348285f12510852037d05c77d54aa0ccf069c361","tid":2041376,"uid":125582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"261b77810ee57060681b43a86e76a490c15d140e","tid":2041376,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"睇嚟班建制個個都支持BNO平權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"班撚樣個個有 反而後生果D好多都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75888fb9413b836000ac7caea6be8ffbc85fd1f4","tid":2041376,"uid":24660,"like"